Occupied house, in which Riesenparties were organized, was vacated
The home-owners had occupied 11 of the 13 apartments in the building at the road Balmes No. 51 (Barcelona).
The twelve squatters left the building afternoon without resistance to have carried out yesterday.
Everything points out that the nightmares of the neighbors of the house No. found 51 at the road Balmes an end.
Twelve persons left yesterday noon voluntarily the building, which illegaly occupied they had kept and had organized in that them enormous celebrations, which had driven the neighborhood to the despair. The evacuation took place on judicial arrangement without without police intervention.
After the evacuation was replaced the door lock, in order to avoid a similar situation.
“From now on the admission will be controlled”, confirmed the house supervisor.
The squatters had occupied, the 11 of the 13 apartments of the building - the remaining were inhabited - carried forward entire electrical system and part of the water supply. In addition they had painted the walls and had left, above all all kinds of garbage doses with alcoholic beverages.
In the three lower floors enormous parties were celebrated, which lasted up to two days and which tenants drove to the despair.
Beside the building is a discotheque, Balmes 51, which carried also damage of it.
Her owner, Maria Pantinat explained Europe presses that their business would have decreased since beginning of the house occupation around 80%.
The owner of the discotheque pointed out that the squatters made their mean competition, because they sold the drinks to three euros, while these cost 10 euros in the discotheque.
In addition the owner of the leisure restaurant had been indicated by the neighbors because of disturbance of the peace, while according to their statement the noise was not due to the visitors of the discotheque, but of the squatters and in particular of the guests of the celebrations, which were organized there, and which according to statements of the annoyed neighbors in the last weeks more and more and longer became.
The responsible person of the discotheque explained that the annoyance had been so large that she came with the owner of the building, to have to pay for the last nine months no rent.
Also the Guardia Urbana (urban police) confirmed likewise that she had received more complaints in the last weeks from the neighbors.
The chairman of the PP (Partido Popular - people's party) in the town councillor Barcelonas, Alberto Fernández Díaz, had demanded last week to vacate the building immediately and to get the problems of civil living together as well as a coming down of the city quarter into the grasp.
He explained that the summer ago only one floor of the building had been occupied, but that the squatters had penetrated in the last months into all floors of the building and nearly all apartments. Into some it had come even to thefts.
In this sense it added that “it was necessary, the impunity an end to set and against the antisocial actions in the building reach through.”
Yesterday a further building in the city quarter Nou Barris was vacated by the katalonischen police.
At 15.30 o'clock approached the police to the road Montral No. 35, after it had received a call from a neighbor, that had observed, how four persons wanted to penetrate into the building.
The four were arrested immediately.
